---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
import User from "./User.astro";
---

<Section id="about" class="mb-24">
  <h2
    class="flex items-center tracking-tight text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold mb-6 gap-x-3"
  >
    <User class="size-8" />
    About
  </h2>
  <article class="flex flex-col gap-5">
    <p class="text-xl text-pretty leading-8">
      I started programming in 2024 after more than 14 years as a lawyer in the
      public and private sectors, following my move from Argentina to Spain.
      Technology has always fascinated me, and as I shifted my career, I
      discovered a new passion. Currently, I divide my time between working as a
      criminal lawyer at a law firm in Madrid and as a frontend developer at a
      Mexican startup.
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl text-pretty leading-8">
      Some of my achievements include
      <span class="font-bold">
        becoming the youngest Court Clerk in the economic criminal court in
        Buenos Aires after being promoted seven times in eight years and
        implementing a digital jurisprudence system that significantly reduced
        errors in legal decision-making.
      </span>
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl text-pretty leading-8">
      As a growing web developer,
      <span class="font-bold">
        I secured my first experience in the field in less than a year
      </span>
      and I am eager to continue learning and evolving in this exciting world of
      technology.
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl text-pretty leading-8">
      Thank you for visiting my portfolio! ðŸš€
    </p>
    <a
      href="#contact"
      role="link"
      class="inline-flex w-fit scroll-smooth items-center px-5 py-2 me-2 mb-2
            text-sm text-gray-900 font-medium rounded-full
            bg-white border border-gray-300
            focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-gray-200
            hover:bg-black hover:scale-110 hover:text-white
            transition
            dark:text-white
            dark:border-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-800
            dark:hover:border-gray-600 dark:hover:bg-gray-700
            dark:focus:ring-gray-700"
    >
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-mail-forward
                        size-5 me-2"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke="currentColor"
        fill="none"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
      >
        <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none" clip-rule="evenodd"
        ></path>
        <path
          d="M12 18h-7a2 2 0 0 1 -2 
                        -2v-10a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h14a2 
                        2 0 0 1 2 2v7.5"
        ></path>
        <path d="M3 6l9 6l9 -6"></path>
        <path d="M15 18h6"></path>
        <path d="M18 15l3 3l-3 3"></path>
      </svg>
      Contact
    </a>
  </article>
</Section>
